<h2 align="center">
<p>Tensorflow 2.0 Implementation of GCViT</p>
</h2>
</p>
<p align="center">
This library implements <b>GCViT</b> using Tensorflow 2.0 specifally in <code>tf.keras.Model</code> manner to get PyTorch flavor.
</p>


